OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with some sunny intervals.
OL,7,FSome clear spells at first tonight but
OL,8,Fclouding over, some mist and low cloud
OL,9,Fin east, perhaps a light shower.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FCloud mostly breaking up in
OL,12,Fthe morning with some sunny spells in
OL,13,Fthe north. Staying cloudier in
OL,14,FSouthern Aberdeenshire, the cloud
OL,15,Fspreading north in the afternoon.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA dry
OL,18,Fand very warm few days with some sunny
OL,19,Fspells. Perhaps some thundery showers
OL,20,Flater on Thursday
